Here is a clean GUI-only procedure for your practical (Windows Server 2022/2025 style). Follow step-by-step exactly.


---

🖥️ PART 1 — DNS CONFIGURATION (GUI)

🔹 1. Open DNS Manager

Click Start → Server Manager

Go to Tools → DNS



---

🔹 2. Create Zone (Micromax.lab)

1. Expand your server name


2. Right-click Forward Lookup Zones → New Zone



Wizard Settings:

Zone Type → ✅ Primary Zone

❌ Uncheck Store the zone in Active Directory

Zone Name:

micromax.lab

Zone File → default (Next)

Dynamic Updates → ❌ Do not allow dynamic updates

Click Finish



---

🔹 3. Create Records

✔ A Record (www)

Right-click inside zone → New Host (A or AAAA)

Name: www

IP: 192.168.x.x

Click Add Host




---

✔ A Record (ftp)

Same steps:

Name: ftp

IP: 192.168.x.x




---

✔ CNAME Record (files)

Right-click → New Alias (CNAME)

Alias name: files

Fully qualified domain name:

ftp.micromax.lab

OK




---

✔ A Record (mailsrv)

New Host:

Name: mailsrv

IP: 192.168.x.x




---

✔ MX Record (mail)

Right-click → Other New Records

Select Mail Exchanger (MX) → Create

Host or child domain: (leave blank or @)

Fully qualified domain name:

mailsrv.micromax.lab

Priority: 10

OK




---

🖥️ PART 2 — DHCP CONFIGURATION (GUI)

🔹 1. Open DHCP Manager

Server Manager → Tools → DHCP



---

🔹 2. Create Scope

1. Expand server → IPv4


2. Right-click IPv4 → New Scope




---

🔹 3. Scope Wizard

Step-by-step:

✔ Name

MicromaxScope

✔ IP Range (100 clients)

Example:

Start IP: 192.168.1.100
End IP:   192.168.1.199

✔ Subnet Mask

Auto-filled → usually:

255.255.255.0

✔ Add Exclusions

→ Skip (Next)

✔ Lease Duration

→ Default (Next)


---

🔹 4. Configure Options (IMPORTANT)

✔ Default Gateway

192.168.1.1

✔ DNS Server

Parent domain:

micromax.lab

DNS Server IP:

(Your Domain Controller IP)

Example: 192.168.1.10



---

🔹 5. Activate Scope

Select Yes, activate this scope



---

✅ TESTING (GUI + CMD)

🔹 On Client Machine

Open Command Prompt:

ipconfig /release
ipconfig /renew

Then:

ping www.micromax.lab
ping ftp.micromax.lab
ping files.micromax.lab


---

⚠️ Practical Tips (Important)

✔ DNS & DHCP must be on same network

✔ Use same IP in A records (server IP)

✔ CNAME must point to FQDN (not IP)

✔ MX must point to hostname (not IP)

✔ Scope must be activated



